extends  ../_skeleton

//- Includes
include ../elements/_ui-panel
include ../elements/_widget-flickrfeed
  include ../elements/_widget-twitter

block variables
  - var activeIndex = 5

block title
  title Blog Post

block page
  // Page Header
  include ../sections/_header-default

  +breadcrumb-classic('images/bg-01.jpg', 'blog',
  {
    0: {
      "title": "Home",
      "href": "./"
    },
    1: {
      "title": "blog",
      "href": "blog.html"
    },
    2:{
      "title": "Blog Post"
    }
  }
  )

  section.section-md.bg-white
    .shell
      h2.text-spacing-0.text-md-left Blog
      .range.range-40.range-md-reverse
        .cell-md-9.cell-lg-8.cell-lg-preffix-1
          .post-blog.text-sm-left
            p.font-accent.big April 10, 2017
            h4 Monday motivation
            .range.range-30
              .cell-xs-12
                img(src="images/single-post-1-770x454.jpg", width="770", height="454", alt="")
              .cell-xs-12
                p Happy Monday! Most people dread Monday, but I like to look at it as the perfect day to start fresh. Whether you've neglected your CrossFit or yoga routine, fallen into bad eating habits, or both - today is the day to get back on track. I get it... juggling work, family time, chores, school and social life can be tough. With events, weddings, appointments and long work hours, it can be easy for some people to put off their time to sweat. But don't let a busy schedule get in the way of regular exercise and nutritious eating. Making your body a priority is possible. Here are some tips to help you stay motivated:
              .cell-xs-12
                ul.list.list-marked.list-marked-type-1.text-left.list-marked-bold
                  li Schedule your workout times in advance as you would any other appointment. Write it down in a calendar, journal or on your phone.
                  li Keep a bag packed with a change of clothes, shoes and all other necessities so you can head straight to your workout without having to stop at home.
                  li Find some fitspiration on Instagram or in magazines. Whether it's pictures of healthy ideas for dinner or a fit body - visuals help!
                  li Keep in touch with your fitfam! Text your trainer, friend, co-worker, or family member at some point during the day to cheer them on or to share what you've accomplished. Having support from those around you gives you a big push towards reaching your goals.
              .cell-xs-12
                .post-meta
                  ul.list-inline.font-accent.text-bold.text-left
                    li
                      span.icon.icon-xs.mdi.mdi-clock.text-primary
                      | 04/25/2017
                    li
                      span.icon.icon-xs.mdi.mdi-comment-multiple-outline.text-primary
                      a(href='#').text-gray-sec 3 comments
                    li
                      span.icon.icon-xs.mdi.mdi-heart-outline.text-primary
                      | 25
                    li
                      span.icon.icon-xs.mdi.mdi-share.text-primary
                      | 11
              .cell-xs-12
                .share-block
                  p.text-bold.font-accent Share this post via
                    a(href='#').icon.big.fa-facebook
                    a(href='#').icon.big.fa-google-plus
                    a(href='#').icon.big.fa-twitter

          .author-block.text-sm-left
            .range.range-30
              .cell-xs-12.text-center
                h4.text-gray-darker About the author
              .cell-xs-12.cell-sm-5.cell-md-4
                img(src="images/single-post-2-270x242.jpg", width="270", height="242", alt="")
              .cell-xs-12.cell-sm-7.cell-md-8
                p I am a professional blogger interested in everything taking place in cyberspace. I am running this website and try my best to make it a better place to visit. I post only the articles that are related to the topic and thoroughly analyze all visitorsâ€™ comments to cater to their needs better. In my articles and blog posts I try to share more information with my readers about CrossFit, yoga, boxing, and workout motivation, and I hope every visitor of this website will find them interesting.
                .button-block
                  a(href='single-member.html').button.button-primary.arrow.arrow-right hire me

          .comment-block.text-left
            h4.text-gray-darker Comments
            .box-comment
              .unit.unit-horizontal
                .unit__left
                  img(src="images/single-post-3-70x70.jpg", width="70", height="70", alt="").icon-circle
                .unit__body
                  p.font-accent.text-gray-darker.text-bold Jessica H. Wheaton #[span.text-gray-sec 15 hours ago]
                  p I thought I knew everything there was to know about "dieting and weight loss". There's literally not a diet or fad I haven't followed. How could I be so wrong? Training with Derick has been the ultimate investment in my health and future.
                  a(href='#').link.arrow.arrow-right.font-accent.text-bold Reply
                  a(href='#').link.arrow.arrow-right.font-accent.text-bold Share

            .box-comment.box-comment-reply
              .unit.unit-horizontal
                .unit__left
                  img(src="images/single-post-4-70x70.jpg", width="70", height="70", alt="").icon-circle
                .unit__body
                  p.font-accent.text-gray-darker.text-bold Ryan K. Moran   #[span.text-gray-sec 9 hours ago]
                  p Under Derick's expert guidance, I began to understand how my body composition, hormones, emotions, stress levels, sleep, nutrition and training were interlinked, and that finding the optimum balance between these elements was the key to weight loss.
                  a(href='#').link.arrow.arrow-right.font-accent.text-bold Reply
                  a(href='#').link.arrow.arrow-right.font-accent.text-bold Share

          .comment-form
            h4.text-gray-darker.text-sm-left Leave a comment
            // RD Mailform
            form.rd-mailform.text-sm-left(data-form-output="form-output-global", data-form-type='contact', method='post', action='bat/rd-mailform.php')

              .form-wrap
                textarea#contact-message.form-input(name="message" data-constraints="@Required")
              .range.range-sm-reverse.range-middle
                .cell-sm-6
                  .form-button.group-sm.text-center.text-sm-right
                    button(type="submit").button.button-primary submit
                .cell-sm-6.text-center.text-sm-left
                  .share-block
                    p.text-bold.font-accent Sign up with
                      a(href='#').icon.big.fa-facebook
                      a(href='#').icon.big.fa-google-plus
                      a(href='#').icon.big.fa-twitter



          .range.text-sm-left
            .cell-xs-12
              ul.pagination-custom
                li.disabled
                  a(href='#').icon.mdi.material-icons-keyboard_backspace
                li.active
                  a(href='#') 1
                li
                  a(href='#') 2
                li
                  a(href='#') 3
                li.dot
                  a(href='#') 4
                li
                  a(href='#') 15
                li
                  a(href='#').icon.mdi.material-icons-keyboard_backspace

        .cell-md-3.cell-lg-3
          .range
            .cell-xs-12.text-md-left
              p.font-accent.big.text-bold.text-gray-darker Search
              // RD Search
              // RD Search
              form.rd-search(action="search-results.html", method="GET", data-search-live="")
                .form-wrap
                  input(class="form-input" id="rd-search-form-input" type="text" name="s" autocomplete="off")
                  button(type='submit').form-search-submit.arrow.arrow-right Search



